{"tid":1644850,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[GTA] FIVEM 孤兒島RP 宣傳","createTime":"2019-10-10T16:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T03:16:08.000Z","uid":55471,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f57b07178a0b85b964c7667105e817bb82da783","tid":1644850,"uid":55471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">孤兒島RP</span></div><br />\n<br />\n伺服器進行緊公測 亦都希望可以透過咁多位玩家既建議 完善我地伺服器既質素 為大家提供一個良好既環境。<br />\n本伺服器唔主張大家搵$，希望大家可以諗多d劇本，大家一齊演戲，令遊戲變得更刺激。<br />\n我地伺服器亦唔似某個共產server咁，一味係度奶班老闆鞋底，處處都幫到班老闆盡，管理員 failRP扮冇野。係我地呢個服，就算係管理員犯規，我地都係一視同仁，按規則處罰。我地本住人人有錢搵既原則，無論係小至一個麵包，大到一層樓，都係以<span style=\"color: red;\">最優惠</span>既價格比大家。<br />\n本伺服器暫時冇打算提供任何課金系統供各位玩家購買，即使有，伺服器團隊亦在此承諾將會以維持伺服器平衡為依歸，請各位玩家放心。<br />\n未來將會加入更多職業，例如殺手，雙黑幫，夜店，保鏢，軍隊等等。。。<br />\n另外我哋即將加入既商店系統，人人都可以做老闆~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲諗？入左黎玩先啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">點擊以下傳送門展開激情對話</span>：<a href=\"https://discord.gg/wPXfB2S\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FwPXfB2S&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5WWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=851ddb89\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/wPXfB2S</a><br />\n<br />\n圖片集：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dcmdeNH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdcmdeNH.png&h=837d4cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/niUqQmH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FniUqQmH.png&h=7cf5442b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緊急車輛以及的士以<span style=\"color: red;\">日本風格</span>作主要特色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQUN3GW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l